**Q12.** Chinese — The San Huang Wu Di (三皇五帝) "Three Sovereigns and Five Emperors" period. Fu Xi, Nüwa, Shennong — are these described as HUMAN or as a different species who ruled before humans? What does Sima Qian's Shiji say about the pre-human or proto-human rulers? Any Chinese tradition of Earth being inhabited by non-human intelligence before the current human civilization?

